<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Elinor Shop - Boutique de Test</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        header {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .header-links a {
            margin-left: 20px;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .header-links a:hover {
            background: #764ba2;
        }

        .products-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .product-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .product-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .product-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            background: #f0f0f0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .product-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .product-info {
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .product-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .product-description {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .product-meta {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
        }

        .product-price {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #667eea;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .product-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            background: #e0f7fa;
            color: #00838f;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .product-badge.in-stock {
            background: #e8f5e9;
            color: #2e7d32;
        }

        .empty-message {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            color: white;
        }

        .empty-message h2 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .info-box {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .info-box h3 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .feed-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .feed-links a {
            padding: 10px 15px;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 13px;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .feed-links a:hover {
            background: #764ba2;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>üõçÔ∏è Elinor Shop</h1>
            <div class="header-links">
                <a href="/admin">Admin</a>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>üì¶ Bienvenue sur Elinor Shop</h3>
            <p>Ceci est une boutique de test pour Google Merchant Center. Vous pouvez g√©rer vos produits et exporter les flux compatibles avec Google Merchant.</p>
            <div class="feed-links">
                <a href="/feed/google-merchant.xml" target="_blank">üì• T√©l√©charger le flux XML</a>
                <a href="/feed/google-merchant.csv" target="_blank">üìä T√©l√©charger le flux CSV</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <% if (products && products.length > 0) { %>
            <div class="products-grid">
                <% products.forEach(product => { %>
                    <div class="product-card">
                        <div class="product-image">
                            <img src="<%= product.image_url %>" alt="<%= product.title %>" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/300?text=Image'">
                        </div>
                        <div class="product-info">
                            <% if (product.availability === 'in_stock') { %>
                                <span class="product-badge in-stock">En stock</span>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <span class="product-badge">Rupture</span>
                            <% } %>
                            <div class="product-title"><%= product.title %></div>
                            <div class="product-description"><%= product.description %></div>
                            <div class="product-meta">
                                <span><%= product.brand || 'N/A' %></span>
                                <span><%= product.category || 'N/A' %></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="product-price"><%= product.price %> <%= product.currency %></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>
        <% } else { %>
            <div class="empty-message">
                <h2>Aucun produit pour le moment</h2>
                <p><a href="/admin" style="color: white; text-decoration: underline;">Allez √† l'administration pour en ajouter</a></p>
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

